TEXT.TITLE: LAND'S END INC <LEYS> VOTES INITIAL PAYOUT
TEXT.BODY: Land's End Inc said its board declared a dividend of 10 cts a share payable April 30, record April 13. It is the company's first dividend since it became a public entity last October. Reuter
